38:23.649 --> 38:25.477
WELL, LIKE YOU SAID,
I'M NEVER GONNA CONVINCE YOU

38:25.520 --> 38:27.348
THAT RED JOHN KILLED
YOUR SISTER.

38:27.392 --> 38:29.829
YOU NEED TO GO AND FIND OUT
THE TRUTH FOR YOURSELF.

38:29.872 --> 38:31.309
BUT, PATRICK--AND WHEN YOU DO,

38:31.352 --> 38:35.356
WHEN YOU KNOW THE TRUTH...

38:35.400 --> 38:37.619
YOU KNOW
WHERE TO FIND ME.

38:37.663 --> 38:41.319
JUST CALL ME.

38:44.713 --> 38:46.454
WHERE ARE THE CAR KEYS?

38:46.498 --> 38:48.326
IN THE CAR.

38:51.416 --> 38:53.374
IS THERE A BACK WAY
OUT OF HERE?

38:53.418 --> 38:56.029
UM, THERE'S--NO.
THERE'S JUST FIRE TRAILS.

38:56.072 --> 38:58.466
OKAY. WHAT ABOUT THIS THING?
DOES THIS RUN?

38:58.510 --> 39:00.468
IT'S BEEN ON A TRICKLE CHARGE.

39:00.512 --> 39:01.643
YEAH, IT SHOULD.

39:01.687 --> 39:03.645
OKAY, YOU TAKE THE 4x4
ON THE FIRE ROAD.

39:03.689 --> 39:04.820
THEY WON'T BE
LOOKING FOR THAT.

39:04.864 --> 39:05.821
I'M GONNA COVER FOR YOU.

39:05.865 --> 39:07.649
YOU CAN'T STAY HERE,
PATRICK.

39:07.693 --> 39:10.348
THERE'S NO WAY THEY'LL BELIEVE
YOU WERE MY HOSTAGE.

39:10.391 --> 39:12.088
I WILL MAKE THEM BELIEVE.

39:12.132 --> 39:13.351
YOU WANT ME TO BEAT YOU UP
OR SOMETHING?

39:13.394 --> 39:15.396
KNOCK YOU OUT?UH, NO, THANKS.

39:24.927 --> 39:25.928
YOU GOTTA GO.

39:29.628 --> 39:31.717
[hood closes]

39:31.760 --> 39:36.069
[engine sputters, turns over]

39:48.951 --> 39:51.084
[engine starts,
door alert chiming]

39:56.568 --> 39:58.526
[seat belt clicks]

39:58.570 --> 39:59.919
[exhales deeply]

40:02.748 --> 40:05.968
[engine revving]

40:06.012 --> 40:09.537
[exhaling deeply]

40:09.581 --> 40:12.671
[engine revs loudly]

40:14.107 --> 40:16.370
[tires screech]

40:22.507 --> 40:25.771
[hissing]

40:30.471 --> 40:32.386
[vehicle approaches]

40:35.128 --> 40:38.653
[car doors close]

40:38.697 --> 40:42.135
