SEARCH THE SURROUNDING WOODS.

40:57.063 --> 40:58.934
JANE.

40:58.978 --> 41:01.371
[groans]HE'S OKAY.

41:01.415 --> 41:02.372
[groans]

41:02.416 --> 41:04.287
DID YOU GET HER?

41:04.331 --> 41:06.681
NOT YET.

41:06.725 --> 41:09.815
SHE'S, UH, SHE'S ON FOOT.

41:09.858 --> 41:11.512
AGENT KIRKLAND,
HOMELAND SECURITY.

41:11.556 --> 41:13.383
I NEED RESCUE HOT
SOUTH OF ORR LAKE,

41:13.427 --> 41:15.037
FOREST ROUTE 42 NORTH 12.[static crackles]

41:15.081 --> 41:17.387
WHO'S THAT GUY?DON'T TALK.

41:17.431 --> 41:18.954
HELP'S ON THE WAY.

41:18.998 --> 41:21.914
[exhales] HURTS.

41:24.873 --> 41:28.398
[groans]SHH. IT'S OKAY.

41:40.019 --> 41:42.325
YOU'LL NEVER KNOW.

41:42.369 --> 41:43.718
I'LL NEVER KNOW WHAT?

41:43.762 --> 41:47.200
WHETHER I ENGINEERED
THE ESCAPE AND ABDUCTION.

41:47.243 --> 41:49.158
TRUST ME. I KNOW.

41:49.202 --> 41:51.509
YOU DON'T KNOW.

41:51.552 --> 41:53.336
YOU JUST GUESS.

41:53.380 --> 41:57.340
AND YOU DIDN'T TELL YOUR NEW
BEST FRIEND, KIRKLAND, EITHER.

41:57.384 --> 41:58.516
I DON'T HAVE ANY EVIDENCE.

41:58.559 --> 42:00.822
IF I DID, I'D PUT YOU
IN CUFFS MYSELF.

42:00.866 --> 42:01.823
NO, YOU WOULDN'T.

42:01.867 --> 42:02.998
TRY ME.

42:03.042 --> 42:06.088
[chuckles]

42:06.132 --> 42:07.089
WHAT'S SO FUNNY?

42:07.133 --> 42:09.527
NOTHING. SORRY.

42:12.312 --> 42:15.445
ALL OF IT'S WORTH IT.

42:22.627 --> 42:26.761
SHE TOLD ME RED JOHN AND I
ARE VERY MUCH ALIKE.

42:26.805 --> 42:28.546
THAT IT'S A WONDER
WE WEREN'T BEST FRIENDS

42:28.589 --> 42:31.461
FROM THE MOMENT
WE SHOOK HANDS.

42:31.505 --> 42:34.247
YOU'VE MET RED JOHN?

42:34.290 --> 42:36.379
YES.

42:36.423 --> 42:39.382
HE'S SOMEONE I KNOW.

42:39.426 --> 42:42.908
[chuckles]
